SUMMARY:Build Enterprise Worthy LLM Inference with Open Source and Kuberne
 tes
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nScaling LLMs to production introduc
 es critical challenges: How do you orchestrate multi-node execution?\n\nOp
 timize GPU scheduling? Achieve low-latency data transfers between nodes? T
 his session reveals how NVIDIA Dynamo and Azure Kubernetes Service solve t
 hese challenges together.\n\nThrough a real-world e-commerce recommendatio
 n scenario\, discover how open-source frameworks and managed Kubernetes un
 lock enterprise-grade inference performance.\n\nLearn to harness advanced 
 hardware like GB200 NVL72\, optimize distributed workloads on AKS\, and de
 liver cost-efficient AI at scale to turn infrastructure complexity into co
 mpetitive advantage.
