SUMMARY:Get Certified: Fabric Data Engineer (DP-700 Accelerated)
DESCRIPTION:Microsoft Reactor Toronto\nThis session was so popular\, we ha
 d to do it again. In this one-hour session\, we’ll walk through the key 
 differences between Synapse and Fabric\, highlight the new concepts covere
 d in the DP-700 exam\, and share practical tips for making the transition.
  You’ll leave with a clear roadmap of what to study\, where to focus.\n\
 n📍 This session is a part of a series. [Learn more here](https://develo
 per.microsoft.com/reactor/series/S-1622/?wt.mc_id=meetup_S-1622_webpage_re
 actor)
